column5: Hi All, As many of you know we have been posting a bunch more stuff on You Tube in the past while. Well our newest video is up. This is a great way for people to see our stuff that don't have WFN and The Score or for people that just want to see more. Please check it out and feel free to rate, comment or subscribe. That's how the you tube world works the more people rate, comment or subscribe your vids the more love they give you. So please check it out and please share it with your friends @ http://www.youtube.com/user/factsoffishing  Happy New Year All!
Those are a lot bigger than the ones we get down this way in the Thames Good Job Dave !!
Very nice Dave!  Happy New Year to you and the family!

Dave, your technique is weak and your skills are lacking...  ...at the game of rock, paper, scissors.  I would destroy you!!!   Seriously though, nice fish.  I've got another reason to go visit my sister in Texas now.

Cool videos on youtube there Dave.  Just wanted to say I'm a really big fan of the show, never miss an episode!  The cast count and fish total are very innovative. Anyone who loves fishing knows everyday on the water isn't a guided trip where "shore lunch" is always included.  Keep up the good work and happy new year!
